snippet.title: COVID-19 update – 22 November, 2021 4pm
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern will give a post-cabinet update at 4pm. She will be joined by the Director-General of Health Dr Ashley Bloomfield.

For the latest information on COVID-19 visit the Unite Against COVID-19 website: https://covid19.govt.nz/

Follow us on social media:
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/UniteAgainstCOVID19/
Twitter https://twitter.com/covid19nz
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/uniteagainstcovid19/
Tik Tok https://www.tiktok.com/@covid19nz?lang=en
